-- India Government Offers 34 Oil, Gas Blocks for Exploration, Notice Shows
-- B y   V   R a m a k r i s h n a n
-- 2010-10-15T01:25:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-15/india-s-government-offers-34-oil-gas-blocks-for-exploration-in-auction.html
India will call for bids for 34 oil
and gas blocks for exploration under its ninth round of such
auctions, according to a Ministry of Petroleum and Natural Gas
advertisement published in the Economic Times newspaper today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
